873
00:32:26,081 --> 00:32:29,862
Esse é seu bisavô.

874
00:32:30,875 --> 00:32:32,815
Meu bisavô?

875
00:32:34,334 --> 00:32:35,634
De verdade?

876
00:32:36,608 --> 00:32:38,416
